---
import Layout from '@layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout title="about me" description="Read more about me" pubDate={new Date('April 04 2026')}>
  <img
    src="blog/about/arian.webp"
    alt="Arian Najafi Yamchelo"
    class="rounded-md object-cover"
  />
  <h2>who i am</h2>
  <p>
    My name is Arian. I'm based in Melbourne, Australia, and I build things with code. I started
    with curiosity about how software works and gradually developed a deeper interest in
    programming, problem-solving, and building systems that are actually useful.
  </p>
  <p>
    I have a habit of over-engineering things — getting too deep into details until a project
    becomes too complicated to finish. Lately I've been working against that, focusing on shipping
    simple, imperfect things rather than waiting for the perfect version that never ships.
  </p>
  <p>This site is where I write about what I'm learning, building, and thinking about.</p>

  <h2>what i do</h2>
  <p>
    I work across software development and AI/ML — building full-stack web applications, training
    and deploying machine learning models, and exploring how the two intersect. My current focus is
    on getting into a graduate role where I can keep developing both sides of that skill set.
  </p>

  <h2>education</h2>
    <h3>monash university</h3>
    <div class="border-secondary rounded-md border p-6 font-mono text-sm">
      <p><span class="text-accent">degree</span> &nbsp; Master of Computer Science</p>
      <p><span class="text-accent">period</span> &nbsp; Mar 2024 – May 2026</p>
      <p>
        <span class="text-accent">focus &nbsp;</span> &nbsp;Artificial Intelligence
      </p>
    </div>
    <h3>rmit university</h3>
    <div class="border-secondary rounded-md border p-6 font-mono text-sm">
      <p>
        <span class="text-accent">degree</span> &nbsp; Bachelor of Information Technology with Distinction
      </p>
      <p><span class="text-accent">period</span> &nbsp; Mar 2021 – Jan 2024</p>
      <p>
        <span class="text-accent">focus &nbsp;</span> &nbsp;Digital Design (Curtin University)
      </p>
    </div>

  <p>
    If you want to get in touch, feel free to reach out via the <a href="/contact" class="no-underline">contact</a> me.
  </p>
</Layout>
